window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>No one would ever envy Robert Burke. He is homeless, destitute, and forced to sleep in the cold, night after night. </b></p> <p>And yet Robert has the love and devotion of his small dog, Scruffy. That is enough to get him through.&nbsp;</p> <p>When Robert meets Scott McKenzie, it changes not this life, but possible future lives. Because Scott takes Robert to Middle Falls, Oregon.&nbsp;</p> <p>Miracles happen in Middle Falls.</p>"; 
